    public abstract class NoteFactory<T extends Enum<T>>
extends Object
    Abstract base class for NaturalisNote factories used by the importers of CSV-like files (BOLD Import, CRS Import, Sample Sheet Import).

    Ayco Holleman

      • setRequiredValue

        protected void setRequiredValue​(NaturalisNote note,
                                NaturalisField field,
                                T column,
                                nl.naturalis.common.base.ThrowingFunction<String,​Object,​InvalidRowException> transformer)
                         throws InvalidRowException
        Transforms the value of the provided column using the provided transformer and then sets the specified field to the transformed value, or throws an InvalidRowException if the row does not have a value for the provided column. Subclasses must not provide transformers that transfor non-null values into null values. Doing so will cause an IllegalArgumentException to be thrown.
